user_data.general_preference: I generally prefer clothing items that are soft, comfortable, and true to size. I value high-quality materials that provide a good fit, especially for everyday wear. Features like stretchiness, breathability, and thoughtful design elements, such as thumbholes in jackets or supportive waistbands in pants, are important to me. On the other hand, I tend to dislike products with poor elastic quality or that do not accommodate curvier body shapes well, as they can lead to discomfort and the need for constant adjustments. Overall, I look for items that combine comfort, style, and practicality.
